## 5. DetailHeader 내부 패턴

### 액션 버튼 (상태별 조건 분기)

```tsx
const isTerminal = TERMINAL_STATUSES.includes(entity.status);
const canEdit = !isTerminal && !entity.isLocked;
const canDelete = !NON_DELETABLE_STATUSES.includes(entity.status);

<Layout.HStack gap="xs" wrap>
  {canEdit && (
    <Button variant="secondary" appearance="outline" size="sm" onClick={handleEdit}>
      <EditIcon size="xs" />
      {t('actions.edit')}
    </Button>
  )}
  {canDelete && (
    <Button variant="secondary" appearance="outline" size="sm" onClick={handleDelete}>
      <DeleteIcon size="xs" />
      {t('actions.delete')}
    </Button>
  )}
</Layout.HStack>
```

### 삭제/파괴 확인 (openOverlay + ResourceActionModal)

```tsx
const handleDelete = async () => {
  const confirmed = await openOverlay({
    component: ResourceActionModal,
    props: {
      actionConfig: {
        title: t('detail.deleteModal.title'),
        subtitle: t('detail.deleteModal.subtitle'),
        actionButtonText: t('detail.deleteModal.action'),
        actionButtonVariant: 'error',
      },
      infoItems: [{ label: t('detail.deleteModal.target'), values: [entity.name], variant: 'gray' }],
    },
  });
  if (confirmed) deleteMutation.mutate(entity.id);
};
```

### 상태 정보 카드 (grid)

```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2">
  <StatusInfoCard
    label={t('detail.info.status')}
    value={t(`status.${entity.status}`)}
    accessory={<StatusIndicator variant={mapStatusToVariant(entity.status)} layout="iconOnly" />}
  />
  <StatusInfoCard label={t('detail.info.type')} value={entity.type} />
</div>
```

