## 6. DetailsTab 패턴 (읽기 전용 정보)

### DetailCard 사용

```tsx
import { DetailCard } from '@thakicloud/shared';

const fields: DetailCardField[] = useMemo(
  () => [
    { label: t('detail.fields.name'), value: entity.name },
    { label: t('detail.fields.status'), value: <StatusIndicator variant={...} label={...} /> },
    { label: t('detail.fields.createdAt'), value: formatAbsoluteTime(entity.createdAt) },
    { label: t('detail.fields.description'), value: entity.description ?? '-' },
  ],
  [entity, t],
);

<DetailCard title={t('detail.overview')} fields={fields} />
```

### InfoBox 사용 (복잡한 값)

```tsx
import { InfoBox } from '@/shared/ui/field';

<InfoBox label={t('detail.fields.endpoint')} value={entity.endpoint} trailing={<CopyButton text={entity.endpoint} />} />
```

